  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37468</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たちは私のことを誰に？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who told you about me?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <StructId>1</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37580</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;ARC&gt;さんに聞きました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We heard it from &lt;ARC&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <StructId>2</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37824</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;ARC&gt;に会ったのか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You met &lt;ARC&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <StructId>3</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37976</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たちの時代にいたということは
２００歳の彼女だな、それは</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So she was in your time... that means she’s 200 years old.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <StructId>4</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38676</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>２００歳……そんなに長く生きるって
どんな気持ちなんだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>200 years old... I wonder what it feels like to live that long.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <StructId>5</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39288</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>人がひとりで生きるには
長すぎる時間だな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It’s far too long for a person to live alone.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <StructId>6</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、仲間がいれば、どんな長い年月だって
きっと乗り越えられる……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But with companions, you can surely overcome even the longest years...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <StructId>7</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、ひとりは……
やっぱり寂しい……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But being alone... is really lonely...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40536</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エト？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Et?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　あ、ううん……&lt;ARC&gt;さん、
どうしてひとりなんだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eh? Ah, um... &lt;ARC&gt;, why are you alone?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <StructId>10</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>一番大切な思い出が彼女の中で大きすぎる。
誰もその穴を埋められない。それどころか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The most important memory is too big within her. No one can fill that hole. Rather...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <StructId>11</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42236</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>人といるとその時のことを思い出して
よけいに彼女を寂しくしてしまうから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Being with people reminds her of that time, which only makes her lonelier.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <StructId>12</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう、なんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishTextIsNull/>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <StructId>13</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42924</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……かもな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...maybe.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <StructId>14</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43404</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_020_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルルル〜……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kurururu~...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <StructId>15</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>14</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
